Benji has routines he likes to follow.

Benji has a bathroom routine. He barks when he needs to go outside in the front to pee.
Benji usually goes poop during his morning walks or his afternoon walks.

Benji has an eating routine.
Benji barks when he really wants to get some people food and has not received a handout yet.

Benji has a daily routine of walking in the morning, resting during the day, hunting for creatures outside in the backyard, walking in the afternoon,
begging for food and using his Yorkie cuteness stare and bark to get handouts, 9pm one last pee before his greenie. After 9pm he finds someplace to 
sleep for the night with a human companion.
